{"tid":1746162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所接獲大量投訴信 人臉辨識公司曠視科技上市聆訊仍未過關","createTime":"2019-11-22T15:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T17:03:39.000Z","uid":78546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f11a70888d8111aeb0f330f73a2508b10f71dcc5","tid":1746162,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191122&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60298443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191122%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60298443&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvghR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=8b0ebb45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191122%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60298443&h=03884c26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191122&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60298443</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被美國列入黑名單的「人臉辨識技術公司」曠視科技，消息指其上市申請仍未能順利通過上市聆訊，需要回答額外問題，包括有沒有充份披露有關美國制裁風險，公司需解釋相關疑慮，才能獲得上市批准。<br />\n<br />\n因應人臉辨識技術在香港所引發的爭議，有網民近日發起「一人一信」活動，去信聯交所指控曠視科技可能違反上市規則。據了解，港交所（388）收到大量相關投訴信。<br />\n<br />\n曠視科技昨日(21日)進行上市聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n曠視科技上市之路一波三折，早前美國商務部把包括曠視科技等多間中國科技公司列入「黑名單」，指公司涉利用高科技監控新疆維吾爾族穆斯林。據《路透社》報道，名單發布後，曠視科技上市聯席保薦人之一的高盛表示，將會審視情况，決定是否繼續參與曠視的承銷工作。"},{"pid":"41d77278af77e9f2fcb11e2492e96916e204b888","tid":1746162,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"行動有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0294db26bf2e53a45c842aa771422eda6fe4540c","tid":1746162,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"和你篤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922a1a8a6706c3dcf63f8bacd3170b5823824a84","tid":1746162,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" cla